### POST Create a new animal (valid request)
POST {{url}}/api/animals
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Elephant",
  "species": "Loxodonta",
  "age": 10,
  "userId": "123"
}

###

### POST Create a new animal (invalid request - missing name)
POST {{url}}/api/animals
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "species": "Loxodonta",
  "age": 10,
  "userId": "123"
}

### Expected response:
### { "error": "Animal name must be provided" }

###

### GET Retrieve all animals
GET {{url}}/api/animals

###

### GET Retrieve specific animal by id (valid)
GET {{url}}/api/animals/1

###

### GET Retrieve specific animal by id (invalid - not found)
GET {{url}}/api/animals/999

### Expected response:
### { "error": "Animal not found" }

###

### PUT Update animal details (valid request)
PUT {{url}}/api/animals/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Elephant",
  "species": "Loxodonta",
  "age": 12
}

###

### PUT Update animal details (invalid request - invalid ID)
PUT {{url}}/api/animals/invalid-id
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Elephant",
  "species": "Loxodonta",
  "age": 12
}

### Expected response:
### { "error": "Invalid animal ID format" }

###

### DELETE Delete specific animal by id (valid)
DELETE {{url}}/api/animals/1

###

### DELETE Delete specific animal by id (not found)
DELETE {{url}}/api/animals/999

### Expected response:
### { "error": "Animal not found" }
